{"tid":1387210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司長與四工會（陰謀論）","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:25:52.000Z","uid":53055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f2474df570cd351decafa1dfedb75228f1206d02","tid":1387210,"uid":53055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"我絕對有理由相信司長已經被四工會威脅，以司長份人唔會鳩衝出黎講道歉，佢講得緊係有高層叫佢咁講，今日開完會既記招正路係由司長做代表對記者講野，但係結果係四工會講完全唔係正常做法。<br />\n所以司長應該係生命受到威脅，所以只能服從工會指示。<br />\n<br />\n現在已經係工會控制國家，各位盡全力做應該做既事。<br />\n<br />\n如果日後我俾工會拉左，好肯定因爲我講既係事實。"},{"pid":"f8d62b73bde53beaf4099526ad63b5d9400c2e68","tid":1387210,"uid":53055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:23:26.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"eafe7536199f5f4f55ecc8141bdf9e38dfb675a3","tid":1387210,"uid":53055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:23:37.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"bc60fcebc9491f47d98a42dfef1d247c9e9f21e9","tid":1387210,"uid":53055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:23:49.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"20e2eb99e8b43cfec94a6ca89f9cb2e742033a83","tid":1387210,"uid":53055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"一隻貓自己推"},{"pid":"d59754ae5003ca2d10b816c360ac0a54687ae25d","tid":1387210,"uid":53055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"本貓要推到上熱門"},{"pid":"533c293979c347f1db5866786e49e850adeb47e9","tid":1387210,"uid":288486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:25:52.000Z","msg":"push"}]}